      <a href="index.html?p=1644#comment-4426"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-08-15T03:45:33-04:00">Sunday, August 15, 2010 at 3:45 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Yum!  The sauce is savory from the reduced chicken broth, and the blossoms give it a sweet, vegetal flavor.  I didn&#39;t have any saffron, but the dish is still delicious without it.  And a perfect use for blossoms that have gotten a bit too limp to stuff 🙂</p>
    </div>

